01:36:56,111 --> 01:36:57,487
Did you dump Bart?
你把巴特甩了吗？

1254
01:36:59,573 --> 01:37:03,576
The Mitsushimi Company of Japan
is ready to make a long-term deal...
日本的三凌公司准备做一个长期合同……

1255
01:37:03,702 --> 01:37:05,620
...with New England Wire and Cable...
……新英格兰电线电缆公司……

1256
01:37:05,912 --> 01:37:09,957
,,, for the production of air bags,
……生产安全气囊，

1257
01:37:10,375 --> 01:37:12,668
I love the sound of your voice.
我喜欢听你的声音

1258
01:37:12,836 --> 01:37:15,672
Well,  here comes the best part,
Lawrence,
嗯，现在这里是最好的部分，劳伦斯，

1259
01:37:16,047 --> 01:37:19,717
You sell Wire and Cable
back to the employees.
你把电线电缆公司卖回给员工

1260
01:37:19,884 --> 01:37:25,973
They modernize and re-equip the plant
and turn out air bags.
他们把工厂的设备做一个现代化地改造并生产安全气囊

1261
01:37:26,099 --> 01:37:27,975
What's in it for me?
我有什么好处?

1262
01:37:28,101 --> 01:37:30,978
They'll pay 28 bucks a share,
他们将支付28美元一股

1263
01:37:31,437 --> 01:37:33,105
You like?
你喜欢吗？

1264
01:37:33,940 --> 01:37:35,816
They'll go to 3O.
股价会到30的

1265
01:37:36,234 --> 01:37:38,736
Thirty? You think so?
30？你这么想？

1266
01:37:39,195 --> 01:37:42,239
Why not? We'll talk about it at dinner.
I'll see you in an hour.
为什么不，我将在晚晚餐时跟你讨论。
我会在一个小时后看到你

1267
01:37:42,657 --> 01:37:45,701
Lunch, tomorrow, 1: OO.
午餐，明天，1点

1268
01:37:45,868 --> 01:37:48,870
You know where. Strictly business.
你知道地方的，纯脆的生意会晤

1269
01:37:49,038 --> 01:37:51,248
Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah. Strictly business.
哦，是，是，是，纯脆的生意会晤

1270
01:37:51,415 --> 01:37:53,250
Wow, did you hear that, Carmen?
哇哦，你听到了吗，卡门？


1271
01:37:53,459 --> 01:37:57,421
Harriet! Call my manicurist,
call the barber, call the florist...
哈丽特，打电话给我的美甲师，理发师，打电话给花店……

1272
01:37:57,588 --> 01:38:00,924
...tell Arthur I want two tickets
to the opera tomorrow night. Puccini.
……告诉亚瑟我要两张明天晚上普契尼的歌剧票

1273
01:38:01,091 --> 01:38:03,426
We're back in business!
我们又回到生意上了

1274
01:38:07,640 --> 01:38:10,184
It's money that I love.
我爱钱


